Cell["\<\
API surface audit: at-a-glance check of which paclet heads compose. \
Operator-like nodes (green) are concentrated at the top; Distance / Predicate \
sinks (purple / red) sit isolated at the bottom of the spiral.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->789401487,ExpressionUUID->"2748a860-ac4f-4cdb-b2ae-619d057ca018"],

